"The MBR installed by the FreeBSD installer is based on [.filename]#/boot/"
"boot0#.  The size and capability of boot0 is restricted to 446 bytes due to "
"the slice table and `0x55AA` identifier at the end of the MBR.  If boot0 and "
"multiple operating systems are installed, a message similar to this example "
"will be displayed at boot time:"
msgstr ""
"El MBR instalado por el instalador de FreeBSD se basa en [.filename]#/boot/"
"boot0#. El tamaño y las capacidades de boot0 está restringido a 446 bytes "
"debido a la tabla de particiones y el identificador `0x55AA` al final del "
"MBR. Si está instalado boot0 y varios sistemas operativos, se mostrará un "
"mensaje similar este durante el arranque:"

